summary: Hey @staff ! I'm a young artist and tumblr is denying me access to people
body:
Hey @staff ! I’m a young artist and tumblr is denying me access to people

Yesterday i made this Fanart [it’s a realistic painting of the valkyrie of Thor Ragnarok, btw totally safe for work].

And, although it had quite a success on my Instagram and my pillowfort i barely had 3 notes on here. I didn’t understand why, so i went through all the tags pages i used to promote my art, and discovered that my artwork, WHILE RESPECTING ALL THE NEW CONSERVATIVES RULES OF TUMBLR, never appeared there.

In consequences, an art work i spent 8 hours of my life for people to see had never, and will never be see.

As my followers base aren’t from the marvel fandom they’ll not share this art (and I don’t mind)so i really relied on the tags to reach people who shared my interrest.

TUMBLR IS denying us to show our art. An art that was never flagged! What have I done wrong????

@wigglebox @winchester-reload @c-kaeru @elizabethrobertajones @magnificent-winged-beast if you don’t mind signal boosting this it would mean a lot…

summary: OTHER PLACES TO FIND ME WHEN THIS WEBSITE (possibly) CEASES TO EXIST.
title: OTHER PLACES TO FIND ME WHEN THIS WEBSITE (possibly) CEASES TO EXIST.
body: Anyhow, I’m staying on Tumblr till it tips over and flatlines. Till that day comes I’ll be on Instagram (@zombiefishu) and Newgrounds (https://zombiefishu.newgrounds.com/). however, I haven't posted anything to Newgrounds yet. But If you really enjoy my art, which I heavily doubt anyone actually does, It would be wise to follow me on these just in case something goes horribly wrong.
